washington  lee university mr smith brings to our board more than  years of experience in the commercial real estate finance industry he has extensive knowledge of our operations having spent his entire career at walker  dunlop in his capacity as president mr smith also provides our board with managements perspective on our business operations and conditions which is crucial to our boards performance of its oversight function source walker  dunlop inc on    sign up for equilar atlas and view howard w smith iiis full profile by accessing equilar atlas you can view bios network salary and wealth events of industryleading executives like howard w smith iii more specifically youll be able to identify corporate executives in howard w smith iiis network and community follow changes in howard w smith iiis employment and moneyinmotion connect with howard w smith iii through your network of conections view full profile   search for over  executive profiles bio example howard w smith iii howard w smith iiis connections  sign up now to view howard w smith iiis  connections » andrew c florance dir chief executive officer and president costar group inc deborah a wilson former executive vice president chief financial officer and treasurer walker  dunlop inc richard c warner executive vice president and chief credit officer walker  dunlop inc alan j bowers former board member la quinta holdings inc cynthia a hallenbeck board member walker  dunlop inc richard m lucas executive vice president general counsel and secretary walker  dunlop inc william m walker chairman of the board and chief executive officer walker  dunlop inc john e rice former board member walker  dunlop inc michael j warren board member walker  dunlop inc stephen p theobald executive vice president chief financial officer and treasurer walker  dunlop inc popular profiles sign up now to view more executive profiles » thomas j lynch executive chairman te connectivity ltd john j kita evp and cfo a o smith carl g annes